{
  "texts": [
    "It could be argued that, at best, we created a system that \"mimics\" human abductive reasoning and provides probable explanations.",
    "This is a complex issue related to the overall opacity of AI systems.",
    "While solving all of this together is outside the scope of this paper, we would like to stress that we do not make only an appeal to abductive aspects of explaining but the social ones as well.",
    "In order to deal with the TG, xAI developers also have to understand that their models ought to be bound to social practices.",
    "While abductions generate explanations of the AI models, these explanations are subject to social norms and standards."
  ]
}